pkg update && pkg upgrade
pkg install ffmpeg imagemagick pandoc

1. For Video and Audio

ffmpeg -i "input" -c copy "output"

Special: (mkv to MP3)
ffmpeg -i "input_video.mkv" -vn -c:a copy "output.m4a"

ffmpeg -i "output.m4a" -q:a 2 "trial.mp3"

2.For Images

magick "input.ext" "output.ext"

For multiple images
magick mogrify -format webp *.jpg

Change webp to the wanted extension and change .jpg to the present one 

3. For Documents

pandoc "input.ext" -o "output.ext
